Package org.apache.guacamole.properties

Interface GuacamoleProperty<Type>

  • Type Parameters:
    Type - The type this GuacamoleProperty will parse into.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanGuacamoleProperty, ByteArrayProperty, EnumGuacamoleProperty, FileGuacamoleProperty, IntegerGuacamoleProperty, LongGuacamoleProperty, StringGuacamoleProperty, StringListProperty, TimeZoneGuacamoleProperty, URIGuacamoleProperty
    public interface GuacamoleProperty<Type>
    An abstract representation of a property in the guacamole.properties file, which parses into a specific type.
